data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS! Welcome to Vanderbilt Reserve, nestled between Vanderbilt Beach Road and Collier Blvd! Minutes from Naples beaches, Mercato, Founder's Square, Downtown 5th Ave and Waterside Shops. Step inside this immaculate END UNIT 2021 built 3- bedrooms, 2.5- bath, with loft “Stanford” and be greeted with a bright, spacious, open concept floorplan. Features include upgraded stainless steel appliances, stunning quartz countertops, under-cabinet kitchen lighting and elegant tile flooring throughout. Enjoy the comfort of a CARPET- FREE second floor! The attached 2- stall garage has finished epoxy floors with extra custom-built storage. Other features include impact resistant windows and doors, whole home dechlorination system for pristine water quality and an underground electric dog fence. Relax outside on the extended covered lanai backing up against the preserve, ensuring privacy. Internet, cable INCLUDED in the HOA fee. Top rated A schools! Only 28 minutes from RSW! Embrace the opportunity to own a home in paradise, that is FULL of upgrades! Bring an offer :)
